### Phase 6 — Search/filters/pagination + dashboard summary

@host = http://localhost:8080
@customerToken = paste-customer-token
@agentToken    = paste-agent-token
@adminToken    = paste-admin-token
@agentUserId   = paste-agent-int64
@createdFrom   = 2026-06-01T00:00:00Z
@createdTo     = 2026-06-30T23:59:59Z

### 1. Default page (per_page=20)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/tickets
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 2. Page 2 with q + status + priority + date range
GET {{host}}/api/v1/tickets?page=2&per_page=10&q=wifi&status=open&priority=high&created_from={{createdFrom}}&created_to={{createdTo}}&sort_by=created_at&sort_order=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 3. Agent's assigned queue
GET {{host}}/api/v1/tickets?view=assigned_to_me
Authorization: Bearer {{agentToken}}

### 4. Admin's "all tickets assigned to a specific agent"
GET {{host}}/api/v1/tickets?view=all&assigned_to={{agentUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 5. Sort by status with stable id tie-breaker
GET {{host}}/api/v1/tickets?sort_by=status&sort_order=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6. Bad sort field — EXPECTED 422
GET {{host}}/api/v1/tickets?sort_by=garbage
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7. Customer tries view=all — EXPECTED 422
GET {{host}}/api/v1/tickets?view=all
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 8. Dashboard summary (role-aware)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

###
GET {{host}}/api/v1/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{agentToken}}

###
GET {{host}}/api/v1/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
